00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:09.577 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:00:09.611 --> 00:00:10.512 position:19% line:89% align:start
[boy] Noon tomorrow...

00:00:10.545 --> 00:00:11.345 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:00:11.378 --> 00:00:13.347 position:27% line:83% align:start
A visitor will be
coming to see you.

00:00:13.380 --> 00:00:15.015 position:13% line:89% align:start
But you must not meet them.

00:00:15.048 --> 00:00:16.216 position:30% line:89% align:start
No matter what

00:00:16.250 --> 00:00:18.753 position:16% line:83% align:start
you absolutely cannot go
to the visiting room.

00:00:18.786 --> 00:00:20.522 position:13% line:89% align:start
There's a visitor for you.

00:00:20.555 --> 00:00:21.656 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:00:22.389 --> 00:00:23.323 position:33% line:89% align:start
[gasps] What?

00:00:23.357 --> 00:00:25.593 position:24% line:83% align:start
Abandon this visit
and go back to your cell.

00:00:26.728 --> 00:00:27.629 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Old man...

00:00:30.598 --> 00:00:32.232 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jotaro] Johngalli A.

00:00:32.266 --> 00:00:34.167 position:33% line:83% align:start
He's the one
who plotted everything.

00:00:34.201 --> 00:00:36.069 position:10% line:89% align:start
In other words, Johngalli A.

00:00:36.103 --> 00:00:37.705 position:24% line:83% align:start
is most definitely
a Stand User.

00:00:37.739 --> 00:00:39.007 position:13% line:89% align:start
All you need to understand

00:00:39.039 --> 00:00:40.875 position:21% line:83% align:start
is that you're being
targeted right now.

00:00:40.909 --> 00:00:43.310 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'll get you out
of here immediately.

00:00:43.343 --> 00:00:46.079 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] The handcuffs.
When did they...?

00:00:46.113 --> 00:00:48.148 position:21% line:83% align:start
Jolyne! Get away from
that door now!

00:00:48.181 --> 00:00:49.584 position:27% line:89% align:start
[grunts in pain]

00:00:49.617 --> 00:00:52.052 position:16% line:89% align:start
Star Platinum: The World!

00:00:53.387 --> 00:00:54.421 position:35% line:89% align:start
Time, stop!

00:00:57.859 --> 00:00:59.059 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:00:59.092 --> 00:01:01.128 position:35% line:89% align:start
[coughing]

00:01:01.161 --> 00:01:03.330 position:30% line:83% align:start
What the fuck?
d I just get shot?

00:01:03.363 --> 00:01:05.667 position:35% line:83% align:start
Don't move!
He's begun his assault.

00:01:07.067 --> 00:01:09.003 position:21% line:83% align:start
So it was reacting to
the air currents

00:01:09.037 --> 00:01:12.105 position:24% line:83% align:start
in order to predict
our location.

00:01:12.139 --> 00:01:14.609 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't move until we know
the mechanism of the snipes.

00:01:14.642 --> 00:01:15.610 position:38% line:89% align:start
We clear?

00:01:15.643 --> 00:01:18.078 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't order me around
like I'm a stupid child.

00:01:18.111 --> 00:01:19.681 position:21% line:83% align:start
-I know that already!
-[guard] Bitch!

00:01:19.714 --> 00:01:22.817 position:33% line:89% align:start
F... FE40536.

00:01:24.052 --> 00:01:26.821 position:27% line:83% align:start
Who do you think
you're talking to, you bitch?

00:01:26.854 --> 00:01:28.656 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Jotaro] Jolyne! [grunts]

00:01:35.697 --> 00:01:36.831 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Are you...?
-Don't move.

00:01:42.503 --> 00:01:45.607 position:24% line:83% align:start
And be sure not to
raise your voice.

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:48.009 position:33% line:83% align:start
It will keep
scouting our location.

00:01:48.042 --> 00:01:49.510 position:10% line:89% align:start
Johngalli A. is able to read

00:01:49.544 --> 00:01:51.913 position:30% line:83% align:start
the flow of air
with that thing.

00:01:51.946 --> 00:01:53.213 position:21% line:83% align:start
It could even be able
to react

00:01:53.246 --> 00:01:55.215 position:30% line:83% align:start
to mild changes
in our breathing.

00:01:56.017 --> 00:01:57.852 position:30% line:83% align:start
And that Stand
is a satellite.

00:01:57.885 --> 00:01:59.386 position:19% line:89% align:start
His sniping satellite,

00:01:59.419 --> 00:02:01.188 position:19% line:83% align:start
where he aims his rifle
at the Stand,

00:02:01.221 --> 00:02:03.123 position:21% line:83% align:start
which then redirects
the bullet.

00:02:03.156 --> 00:02:05.292 position:30% line:83% align:start
Johngalli A. is
in the men's prison.

00:02:05.325 --> 00:02:07.695 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's no way we can
attack him from this room,

00:02:07.729 --> 00:02:11.099 position:24% line:83% align:start
so instead we have
to smash his satellite Stand.

00:02:11.131 --> 00:02:13.101 position:10% line:83% align:start
Because any damage inflicted
on the Stand

00:02:13.133 --> 00:02:14.802 position:21% line:83% align:start
is passed through to
the User as well.

00:02:15.235 --> 00:02:16.470 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I know.

00:02:16.504 --> 00:02:20.240 position:19% line:83% align:start
But... the problem is,
when we move to strike it,

00:02:20.273 --> 00:02:21.475 position:33% line:83% align:start
the change in
the air current

00:02:21.509 --> 00:02:23.077 position:10% line:89% align:start
will give him our locations,

00:02:23.111 --> 00:02:24.846 position:24% line:83% align:start
and he'll attack us
immediately.

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:25.813 position:27% line:89% align:start
[grunts in pain]

00:02:25.847 --> 00:02:27.815 position:21% line:89% align:start
[tense music playing]

00:02:27.849 --> 00:02:28.816 position:30% line:89% align:start
[stiff exhale]

00:02:29.684 --> 00:02:30.551 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:02:38.026 --> 00:02:39.694 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[determined grunt]
-[whoosh]

00:02:42.130 --> 00:02:43.865 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't move away
from the wall, Jolyne!

00:02:44.766 --> 00:02:46.233 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's actively hunting you!

00:02:47.001 --> 00:02:48.770 position:41% line:89% align:start
Jolyne.

00:02:50.004 --> 00:02:51.238 position:24% line:89% align:start
What are you doing?

00:02:52.940 --> 00:02:54.474 position:10% line:89% align:start
[opening theme song playing]

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:43.785 position:19% line:89% align:start
[footsteps approaching]

00:04:46.921 --> 00:04:49.489 position:21% line:89% align:start
[tense music playing]

00:04:52.794 --> 00:04:53.961 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clicking]

00:04:55.830 --> 00:04:57.732 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeaking]

00:04:59.133 --> 00:05:00.268 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Johngalli]
I can hardly afford

00:05:00.300 --> 00:05:01.936 position:10% line:89% align:start
to place my faith in muscles.

00:05:02.837 --> 00:05:04.872 position:16% line:83% align:start
When the skin is exposed
to the wind,

00:05:04.906 --> 00:05:06.406 position:19% line:89% align:start
muscles become stressed

00:05:06.439 --> 00:05:09.342 position:13% line:83% align:start
and cause subtle expansions
and contractions.

00:05:09.376 --> 00:05:11.279 position:21% line:83% align:start
These minor movements
are ones

00:05:11.311 --> 00:05:13.114 position:10% line:89% align:start
that the body cannot control.

00:05:13.147 --> 00:05:14.314 position:38% line:89% align:start
[clicks]

00:05:14.347 --> 00:05:17.685 position:24% line:83% align:start
I support the rifle
with bone.

00:05:17.718 --> 00:05:20.420 position:27% line:83% align:start
The bone embraces
the certainty of the ground,

00:05:20.453 --> 00:05:22.523 position:10% line:89% align:start
and the gun unifies with it.

00:05:22.557 --> 00:05:24.792 position:27% line:83% align:start
I place my trust
in that stability.

00:05:25.526 --> 00:05:27.094 position:24% line:89% align:start
Meteorologists say

00:05:27.128 --> 00:05:29.096 position:30% line:83% align:start
wind movements
are unpredictable,

00:05:29.130 --> 00:05:30.631 position:19% line:89% align:start
and they have a point.

00:05:30.665 --> 00:05:33.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
But that doesn't mean
it's impossible.

00:05:33.201 --> 00:05:34.168 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clicking]

00:05:34.202 --> 00:05:35.503 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[buzzing]
-[metal clinks]

00:05:35.536 --> 00:05:38.873 position:13% line:83% align:start
Is this fly simply buzzing
around aimlessly in space?

00:05:39.907 --> 00:05:40.641 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hardly.

00:05:40.675 --> 00:05:43.144 position:24% line:83% align:start
This fly is guided
by the smell

00:05:43.177 --> 00:05:45.412 position:24% line:83% align:start
and flow of the air
as it flies.

00:05:45.445 --> 00:05:47.849 position:10% line:83% align:start
For the wind is the movement
of the fly.

00:05:49.283 --> 00:05:50.818 position:38% line:89% align:start
[buzzing]

00:05:53.254 --> 00:05:54.121 position:38% line:89% align:start
[clanks]

00:05:56.224 --> 00:05:58.159 position:27% line:89% align:start
[labored buzzing]

00:05:58.192 --> 00:06:00.161 position:19% line:89% align:start
Just as the guard said,

00:06:00.194 --> 00:06:02.129 position:16% line:89% align:start
Jotaro Kujo has appeared.

00:06:03.231 --> 00:06:04.932 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's here visiting
his daughter,

00:06:04.966 --> 00:06:06.334 position:33% line:89% align:start
Jolyne Cujoh,

00:06:06.366 --> 00:06:10.104 position:19% line:83% align:start
which means two bearers
of the Joestar bloodline

00:06:10.137 --> 00:06:11.806 position:13% line:89% align:start
are in that visiting room,

00:06:11.839 --> 00:06:15.810 position:16% line:83% align:start
placing them within range
of my Downtown Transfer!

00:06:16.644 --> 00:06:21.682 position:27% line:83% align:start
Joestar, Joestar,
Joestar, Joestar!

00:06:21.716 --> 00:06:24.417 position:27% line:83% align:start
When I've finally
erased your legacy,

00:06:24.451 --> 00:06:27.255 position:30% line:83% align:start
only then will
my life truly begin!

00:06:27.288 --> 00:06:29.456 position:38% line:83% align:start
At last,
I will exact my vengeance

00:06:29.489 --> 00:06:33.393 position:21% line:83% align:start
for you robbing me of
my heart's support!

00:06:33.426 --> 00:06:35.930 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[exhales]
-[fire alarm ringing]

00:06:35.963 --> 00:06:38.666 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[water splashing]
-[ringing continues]

00:06:47.041 --> 00:06:48.075 position:38% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:06:48.109 --> 00:06:49.442 position:27% line:89% align:start
[metal clanking]

00:06:49.476 --> 00:06:50.845 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jotaro] I see...

00:06:50.878 --> 00:06:53.714 position:13% line:83% align:start
You said we needed to take
this thing out, is that right?

00:06:53.748 --> 00:06:54.715 position:38% line:89% align:start
Watch it.

00:06:54.749 --> 00:06:56.717 position:19% line:83% align:start
The droplets are making
it move erratically

00:06:56.751 --> 00:06:58.819 position:19% line:83% align:start
because it can't detect
the air flow!

00:06:58.853 --> 00:06:59.687 position:44% line:89% align:start
Now!

00:07:00.121 --> 00:07:01.989 position:33% line:89% align:start
Stone Ocean!

00:07:02.023 --> 00:07:04.091 position:13% line:89% align:start
Wait, Jolyne! Look closer!

00:07:04.125 --> 00:07:05.026 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:07.061 --> 00:07:10.598 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Jotaro] It's dodging the drops
of water one by one.

00:07:10.631 --> 00:07:12.499 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's reading the shifts
in the air current

00:07:12.533 --> 00:07:13.801 position:21% line:89% align:start
caused by the drops.

00:07:13.834 --> 00:07:17.470 position:10% line:83% align:start
Jolyne, get back to the wall
before it shoots you.

00:07:18.940 --> 00:07:20.440 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshes]

00:07:20.942 --> 00:07:22.076 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, this blows.

00:07:22.109 --> 00:07:23.411 position:16% line:89% align:start
Once the guards get here,

00:07:23.443 --> 00:07:25.212 position:33% line:83% align:start
the air will
all shift at once.

00:07:26.113 --> 00:07:27.515 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ringing]

00:07:28.481 --> 00:07:29.917 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[knocking]
-[startled exhale]

00:07:29.951 --> 00:07:32.586 position:7% line:83% align:start
-[boy] Jolyne, you must listen.
-Huh?

00:07:34.021 --> 00:07:36.223 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hurry! You have to move
the stone block

00:07:36.257 --> 00:07:37.091 position:10% line:89% align:start
at the bottom of the pillar!

00:07:37.124 --> 00:07:38.926 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hit it with all you've got!

00:07:39.527 --> 00:07:40.561 position:35% line:89% align:start
You again?

00:07:40.594 --> 00:07:42.797 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't worry about me!
Just do it!

00:07:42.830 --> 00:07:45.599 position:21% line:83% align:start
Got it? Don't forget
what I told you!

00:07:45.633 --> 00:07:47.134 position:33% line:83% align:start
I want you to
make it through this.

00:07:49.337 --> 00:07:50.838 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cracking]

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:54.942 position:30% line:83% align:start
I have no idea
what's going on,

00:07:54.976 --> 00:07:56.978 position:24% line:83% align:start
but this hole here
between the walls

00:07:57.011 --> 00:07:58.212 position:27% line:89% align:start
leads down there.

00:07:58.245 --> 00:07:59.847 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's some kind of passageway.

00:08:00.648 --> 00:08:02.249 position:33% line:83% align:start
Perhaps into
the prison sewers.

00:08:02.984 --> 00:08:04.385 position:24% line:89% align:start
Or through a vent?

00:08:04.418 --> 00:08:05.653 position:13% line:89% align:start
Where the hell does it go?

00:08:05.686 --> 00:08:08.356 position:27% line:83% align:start
For all we know,
it could lead outside.

00:08:08.389 --> 00:08:10.691 position:27% line:83% align:start
Let's go, Jolyne.
We haven't got a choice.

00:08:13.127 --> 00:08:14.829 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

00:08:16.764 --> 00:08:18.833 position:30% line:83% align:start
-It went away.
-No, it didn't!

00:08:18.866 --> 00:08:20.401 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's close.

00:08:20.434 --> 00:08:22.336 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's merely attempting
to determine

00:08:22.370 --> 00:08:23.504 position:13% line:89% align:start
the perfect shooting angle.

00:08:23.537 --> 00:08:24.605 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're wrong.

00:08:25.740 --> 00:08:27.908 position:21% line:89% align:start
It went to chase him.

00:08:27.942 --> 00:08:29.910 position:16% line:83% align:start
The boy on the other side
of this door.

00:08:30.845 --> 00:08:32.480 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's trying to kill the boy

00:08:32.513 --> 00:08:34.382 position:27% line:83% align:start
who told us about
the secret passageway.

00:08:34.415 --> 00:08:36.350 position:24% line:89% align:start
Jolyne, take cover!

00:08:36.384 --> 00:08:37.385 position:27% line:89% align:start
I came here today

00:08:37.418 --> 00:08:38.953 position:24% line:83% align:start
to help you get out
of this place!

00:08:39.887 --> 00:08:40.821 position:30% line:89% align:start
[glass clinks]

00:08:40.855 --> 00:08:42.890 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:08:48.596 --> 00:08:50.798 position:13% line:89% align:start
Before I came to this room,

00:08:51.866 --> 00:08:52.900 position:35% line:89% align:start
that boy...

00:08:52.933 --> 00:08:56.804 position:27% line:83% align:start
He grabbed my arm
as I walked by. He did.

00:08:57.905 --> 00:09:00.041 position:33% line:83% align:start
As strange as
it may seem, he's here.

00:09:01.108 --> 00:09:03.844 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just an ordinary kid
like you'd see in the park

00:09:03.878 --> 00:09:07.014 position:13% line:83% align:start
and a total stranger to me,
for whatever it's worth.

00:09:07.848 --> 00:09:08.682 position:35% line:89% align:start
And yet...

00:09:08.716 --> 00:09:11.285 position:27% line:83% align:start
He grabbed me as
if he depended on me.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:14.722 position:13% line:89% align:start
It was strangely soothing.

00:09:14.755 --> 00:09:17.024 position:19% line:83% align:start
The warmth of his hand
holding my arm.

00:09:17.758 --> 00:09:20.628 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's why I'm going back in.

00:09:20.661 --> 00:09:22.329 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm gonna defeat Johngalli A.

00:09:23.297 --> 00:09:25.166 position:27% line:83% align:start
before he shoots
that poor kid.

00:09:26.400 --> 00:09:27.268 position:38% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:09:29.203 --> 00:09:30.137 position:35% line:89% align:start
Good grief.

00:09:31.639 --> 00:09:33.340 position:16% line:89% align:start
[sinister music playing]

00:09:36.710 --> 00:09:38.345 position:13% line:89% align:start
[guard 1] Check visitation!

00:09:38.379 --> 00:09:40.515 position:16% line:83% align:start
The fire alarm is coming
from there!

00:09:40.549 --> 00:09:41.816 position:38% line:83% align:start
[guard 2]
I don't know the situation,

00:09:41.849 --> 00:09:42.783 position:21% line:89% align:start
because there's no...

00:09:42.817 --> 00:09:44.618 position:19% line:89% align:start
Where? Where did he go?

00:09:48.355 --> 00:09:49.323 position:35% line:89% align:start
That boy...

00:09:49.356 --> 00:09:50.825 position:21% line:83% align:start
Where the hell did he
come from?

00:09:50.858 --> 00:09:53.828 position:24% line:83% align:start
And how was he able
to just disappear like that?

00:09:58.833 --> 00:10:00.634 position:10% line:89% align:start
[guard 1] Hurry! It's room B!

00:10:02.636 --> 00:10:04.105 position:30% line:89% align:start
[metal clinks]

00:10:05.673 --> 00:10:07.108 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[wind howling]
-[gasps]

00:10:07.141 --> 00:10:10.244 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did he dig this hole?
In this wall?

00:10:10.277 --> 00:10:11.946 position:13% line:89% align:start
He must have gone in here.

00:10:17.552 --> 00:10:18.886 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Johngalli]
This one's height is

00:10:18.919 --> 00:10:20.421 position:21% line:83% align:start
roughly four and half
eet tall.

00:10:20.454 --> 00:10:22.790 position:16% line:89% align:start
He's small. Like a child.

00:10:24.258 --> 00:10:25.759 position:19% line:89% align:start
I don't know who he is,

00:10:25.793 --> 00:10:28.496 position:27% line:83% align:start
but the hole that
suddenly opened is a vent.

00:10:28.530 --> 00:10:29.930 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can tell right
where it leads

00:10:29.964 --> 00:10:31.533 position:10% line:89% align:start
by the movement of the wind.

00:10:31.566 --> 00:10:33.000 position:33% line:89% align:start
But still...

00:10:33.033 --> 00:10:34.869 position:21% line:83% align:start
I must do everything
in my power

00:10:34.902 --> 00:10:35.970 position:13% line:89% align:start
to prevent that little guy

00:10:36.003 --> 00:10:38.105 position:33% line:83% align:start
from guiding
Jotaro and Jolyne

00:10:38.139 --> 00:10:39.840 position:27% line:83% align:start
to the vent where
my bullets have

00:10:39.874 --> 00:10:42.042 position:16% line:89% align:start
no hope of reaching them!

00:10:42.076 --> 00:10:44.111 position:21% line:83% align:start
I will not lose sight
of them any longer!

00:10:44.145 --> 00:10:47.114 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll shoot down
that little brat first!

00:10:49.416 --> 00:10:50.851 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Jotaro] Jolyne...

00:10:50.885 --> 00:10:53.754 position:27% line:83% align:start
The situation has
gotten too heavy.

00:10:53.787 --> 00:10:56.190 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now the Stand can only
be used for defense.

00:10:57.391 --> 00:10:58.726 position:19% line:89% align:start
If we try to attack it,

00:10:58.759 --> 00:11:00.694 position:16% line:83% align:start
it will detect the change
in air flow.

00:11:01.362 --> 00:11:02.930 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's way too heavy.

00:11:03.632 --> 00:11:04.698 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hey, you!

00:11:04.732 --> 00:11:06.233 position:21% line:83% align:start
You aren't allowed to
leave visitation!

00:11:06.267 --> 00:11:07.301 position:16% line:89% align:start
This is the prison side!

00:11:07.334 --> 00:11:09.504 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[sighs] Good grief.
-Visitors must remain on...

00:11:09.538 --> 00:11:12.740 position:27% line:89% align:start
What the--? Huh?

00:11:13.340 --> 00:11:15.376 position:24% line:89% align:start
[labored breathing]

00:11:21.550 --> 00:11:22.416 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:11:26.754 --> 00:11:28.956 position:7% line:89% align:start
[gasps] That thing is here too!

00:11:33.093 --> 00:11:35.396 position:21% line:83% align:start
It really is hunting
for that kid.

00:11:36.330 --> 00:11:37.464 position:21% line:83% align:start
But how does he plan
to shoot

00:11:37.498 --> 00:11:38.600 position:33% line:83% align:start
a bullet from
the men's prison

00:11:38.633 --> 00:11:40.901 position:24% line:83% align:start
into a utility room
that has no windows?

00:11:41.869 --> 00:11:44.606 position:16% line:89% align:start
What? Hold on, is he...?

00:11:44.639 --> 00:11:48.008 position:10% line:89% align:start
[gasps] That hatch... Clever!

00:11:48.742 --> 00:11:49.910 position:30% line:89% align:start
Nice work, kid.

00:11:49.944 --> 00:11:52.614 position:24% line:83% align:start
I just hope you're
as lucky as you are smart.

00:11:52.647 --> 00:11:54.549 position:21% line:83% align:start
If his entire body is
in the water,

00:11:54.583 --> 00:11:55.749 position:13% line:89% align:start
there are no air currents.

00:11:55.783 --> 00:11:57.619 position:13% line:89% align:start
Especially inside the pipe.

00:11:57.652 --> 00:12:00.287 position:21% line:83% align:start
Looks like it already
lost sight of him too.

00:12:00.321 --> 00:12:02.790 position:10% line:83% align:start
And there aren't any windows
in this room.

00:12:02.823 --> 00:12:04.825 position:30% line:83% align:start
There's no way
he can shoot--

00:12:05.259 --> 00:12:06.026 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:12:06.927 --> 00:12:10.798 position:35% line:83% align:start
That pipe!
But why... and from where?

00:12:12.766 --> 00:12:14.034 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[boom]
-[metal clanks]

00:12:15.302 --> 00:12:16.170 position:30% line:89% align:start
You're kidding!

00:12:18.439 --> 00:12:19.507 position:24% line:89% align:start
[anxiously exhales]

00:12:23.612 --> 00:12:24.478 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:12:26.615 --> 00:12:27.781 position:21% line:89% align:start
[bullet shell clanks]

00:12:27.815 --> 00:12:30.184 position:21% line:89% align:start
Distance, 321 meters.

00:12:30.217 --> 00:12:33.320 position:21% line:83% align:start
The bullet drops 9.5
centimeters in transit.

00:12:33.354 --> 00:12:36.323 position:16% line:83% align:start
Wind speed of 3.2 meters
from the right.

00:12:36.357 --> 00:12:39.827 position:19% line:83% align:start
This shifts the bullet
4.2 centimeters left.

00:12:40.629 --> 00:12:42.062 position:24% line:89% align:start
Target identified.

00:12:42.096 --> 00:12:44.898 position:19% line:83% align:start
Point of aim is locked
on his heart.

00:12:44.932 --> 00:12:47.268 position:19% line:89% align:start
Watch out! Stone Ocean!

00:12:50.337 --> 00:12:51.372 position:30% line:89% align:start
Those threads!

00:12:51.405 --> 00:12:53.007 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's Jolyne Cujoh.

00:12:53.040 --> 00:12:54.975 position:7% line:89% align:start
I clearly recognize her Stand.

00:12:55.009 --> 00:12:57.144 position:27% line:83% align:start
She's just jumped
out of cover!

00:12:57.177 --> 00:12:58.879 position:27% line:89% align:start
Is she an idiot?

00:12:58.912 --> 00:13:00.914 position:27% line:83% align:start
You really think
that will save you?

00:13:00.948 --> 00:13:03.618 position:21% line:83% align:start
Shifting point of aim
to Jolyne!

00:13:03.652 --> 00:13:05.252 position:24% line:89% align:start
Head shot lined up!

00:13:06.186 --> 00:13:07.888 position:27% line:89% align:start
Now say "cheese"!

00:13:13.728 --> 00:13:14.795 position:38% line:89% align:start
[clinks]

00:13:17.431 --> 00:13:18.332 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:13:19.133 --> 00:13:21.302 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[upbeat music playing]

00:13:23.738 --> 00:13:25.306 position:41% line:83% align:start
-What?
-[coughs]

00:13:25.873 --> 00:13:27.875 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well, look at that.

00:13:27.908 --> 00:13:30.210 position:27% line:83% align:start
Glad I broke that
pipe earlier. [coughs]

00:13:30.844 --> 00:13:31.812 position:24% line:89% align:start
[strains] When I...

00:13:31.845 --> 00:13:34.214 position:19% line:83% align:start
busted the pipe coming
in here.

00:13:34.248 --> 00:13:36.584 position:27% line:83% align:start
I remembered some
basic science.

00:13:36.618 --> 00:13:38.018 position:24% line:89% align:start
Gas is lightweight,

00:13:38.052 --> 00:13:40.321 position:19% line:83% align:start
so when it accumulates
around a given area,

00:13:40.354 --> 00:13:42.856 position:13% line:83% align:start
it can create a completely
separate air flow,

00:13:42.890 --> 00:13:44.592 position:19% line:83% align:start
which would put you at
a disadvantage

00:13:44.626 --> 00:13:45.794 position:16% line:89% align:start
reading the air currents.

00:13:45.826 --> 00:13:46.728 position:38% line:89% align:start
[coughs]

00:13:46.761 --> 00:13:47.895 position:24% line:89% align:start
Guess I was right.

00:13:48.530 --> 00:13:50.665 position:16% line:89% align:start
[grunts] What did you do?

00:13:50.699 --> 00:13:51.832 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's over!

00:13:51.865 --> 00:13:53.233 position:16% line:89% align:start
I've already caught you!

00:13:53.668 --> 00:13:55.869 position:33% line:89% align:start
Stone Ocean!

00:13:57.505 --> 00:13:59.507 position:27% line:89% align:start
[groans in pain]

00:14:00.240 --> 00:14:01.375 position:27% line:89% align:start
[metal clatters]

00:14:01.408 --> 00:14:04.278 position:19% line:83% align:start
Seems like Johngalli A.
couldn't read his own luck.

00:14:12.086 --> 00:14:13.954 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[clatters]
-[gasps]

00:14:15.422 --> 00:14:16.490 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey, who are you?

00:14:17.491 --> 00:14:19.226 position:24% line:83% align:start
And how the hell is
a little kid like you

00:14:19.259 --> 00:14:21.862 position:24% line:83% align:start
able to move freely
around this prison?

00:14:23.732 --> 00:14:24.799 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cracks]

00:14:24.833 --> 00:14:27.201 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:14:27.234 --> 00:14:28.102 position:35% line:89% align:start
That hurt.

00:14:29.970 --> 00:14:31.105 position:33% line:89% align:start
This thing...

00:14:31.138 --> 00:14:33.808 position:33% line:83% align:start
That's right.
You gave this to me earlier.

00:14:33.842 --> 00:14:35.677 position:33% line:89% align:start
What is this?

00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:37.211 position:10% line:89% align:start
Looks like some kind of bone.

00:14:37.244 --> 00:14:39.012 position:10% line:89% align:start
Why did you hand this to me?

00:14:39.046 --> 00:14:41.181 position:21% line:83% align:start
You told me not to go
to the visiting room.

00:14:41.215 --> 00:14:43.150 position:30% line:83% align:start
How do you know
so much about me?

00:14:43.718 --> 00:14:44.586 position:33% line:89% align:start
[small gasp]

00:14:45.352 --> 00:14:46.253 position:27% line:89% align:start
I want an answer!

00:14:46.286 --> 00:14:50.124 position:35% line:83% align:start
In time...
things will be... revealed.

00:14:50.157 --> 00:14:51.793 position:30% line:83% align:start
Just hold onto
what I gave you,

00:14:51.826 --> 00:14:52.960 position:30% line:89% align:start
no matter what.

00:14:55.764 --> 00:14:59.199 position:5% line:89% align:start
The smell... is that your doing?

00:14:59.233 --> 00:15:02.069 position:35% line:83% align:start
I captured
Johngalli A.'s sniper Stand.

00:15:02.102 --> 00:15:04.371 position:24% line:83% align:start
He wasn't so tough
when I had it in my net.

00:15:05.205 --> 00:15:07.609 position:41% line:83% align:start
And so,
I smashed it to pieces.

00:15:07.642 --> 00:15:08.108 position:21% line:89% align:start
[theme song playing]

00:15:08.142 --> 00:15:09.109 position:41% line:89% align:start
I see.

00:15:09.143 --> 00:15:10.812 position:7% line:83% align:start
It would appear you've already
grown accustomed

00:15:10.845 --> 00:15:13.013 position:19% line:83% align:start
accustomed to fighting
using your Stand.

00:15:13.046 --> 00:15:15.382 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's not like
I wanted to. [gasps]

00:15:19.219 --> 00:15:20.387 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:21.955 --> 00:15:24.024 position:21% line:89% align:start
[breathes nervously]

00:15:24.057 --> 00:15:27.261 position:13% line:83% align:start
He's in here! Behind that!
I just saw him moving!

00:15:29.930 --> 00:15:32.299 position:7% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Hide! He has a rifle!

00:15:32.332 --> 00:15:34.067 position:33% line:83% align:start
He's up there
behind that pipe!

00:15:34.101 --> 00:15:36.136 position:24% line:83% align:start
He crawled up above
that tank.

00:15:36.170 --> 00:15:38.305 position:16% line:89% align:start
That would be impossible.

00:15:38.338 --> 00:15:39.841 position:33% line:83% align:start
He fired from
the men's prison,

00:15:39.874 --> 00:15:42.209 position:10% line:83% align:start
which is two to three hundred
meters away.

00:15:42.911 --> 00:15:44.813 position:10% line:89% align:start
Add in dozens of steel bars,

00:15:44.846 --> 00:15:46.980 position:27% line:83% align:start
and the fact that
the man is almost blind,

00:15:47.014 --> 00:15:48.650 position:19% line:83% align:start
how in the world would
he have been able

00:15:48.683 --> 00:15:49.717 position:19% line:89% align:start
to get here so quickly?

00:15:49.751 --> 00:15:52.953 position:19% line:83% align:start
No idea, but I saw him
in here with us!

00:15:52.986 --> 00:15:54.488 position:27% line:89% align:start
Get down! [gasps]

00:15:55.757 --> 00:15:58.225 position:19% line:83% align:start
He's in the crawl space
above you!

00:15:59.561 --> 00:16:01.663 position:19% line:89% align:start
Very well. I trust you.

00:16:02.396 --> 00:16:03.330 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ora!

00:16:03.363 --> 00:16:04.532 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:16:04.566 --> 00:16:06.233 position:27% line:89% align:start
Prepare yourself.

00:16:06.266 --> 00:16:08.603 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm sure enough gas
has accumulated by now.

00:16:16.343 --> 00:16:17.344 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:16:17.377 --> 00:16:18.646 position:38% line:89% align:start
[clanks]

00:16:18.680 --> 00:16:20.013 position:35% line:89% align:start
We did it!

00:16:20.047 --> 00:16:22.617 position:10% line:83% align:start
Hey, the coast is clear now!
Huh?

00:16:22.650 --> 00:16:23.518 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:16:24.151 --> 00:16:26.286 position:16% line:89% align:start
The kid... where'd he go?

00:16:27.689 --> 00:16:29.557 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hey, you can come out.

00:16:29.591 --> 00:16:31.358 position:10% line:89% align:start
We took care of the bad guy!

00:16:31.391 --> 00:16:33.828 position:33% line:83% align:start
Come out and
tell me what's going on!

00:16:33.862 --> 00:16:35.597 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey, what are you doing?

00:16:35.630 --> 00:16:36.798 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm looking for the kid!

00:16:36.831 --> 00:16:40.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did you happen to see
which way the little boy went?

00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:42.770 position:24% line:83% align:start
I don't understand
what you're asking.

00:16:42.804 --> 00:16:44.772 position:30% line:83% align:start
Who's this boy
you're talking about?

00:16:44.806 --> 00:16:46.073 position:38% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:16:46.975 --> 00:16:48.275 position:24% line:89% align:start
There was this kid.

00:16:48.308 --> 00:16:50.778 position:16% line:83% align:start
How could you not see him
in his baseball gear?

00:16:50.812 --> 00:16:51.980 position:13% line:89% align:start
That's who I was talking to

00:16:52.012 --> 00:16:53.681 position:30% line:83% align:start
when we were in
the visiting room.

00:16:53.715 --> 00:16:54.649 position:27% line:89% align:start
It was this boy.

00:16:54.682 --> 00:16:57.117 position:10% line:83% align:start
Johngalli A. was even trying
to kill this kid

00:16:57.150 --> 00:16:58.520 position:19% line:89% align:start
for getting in his way.

00:16:58.553 --> 00:17:00.320 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kill him?

00:17:00.354 --> 00:17:03.323 position:19% line:83% align:start
Seriously, I don't know
what you're talking about.

00:17:03.357 --> 00:17:06.895 position:16% line:83% align:start
You came all the way down
to this room on your own.

00:17:06.928 --> 00:17:09.029 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's why I decided to
follow you down.

00:17:09.062 --> 00:17:11.933 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] Hang on.
That doesn't make any sense.

00:17:11.966 --> 00:17:14.401 position:24% line:83% align:start
You should've heard
the boy's voice at least.

00:17:14.434 --> 00:17:16.738 position:30% line:83% align:start
There's no way
you wouldn't have heard him!

00:17:16.771 --> 00:17:17.906 position:16% line:89% align:start
He's the one who told us

00:17:17.939 --> 00:17:19.841 position:16% line:83% align:start
about the secret passage
in the first place.

00:17:19.874 --> 00:17:22.175 position:10% line:89% align:start
We talked about it, remember?

00:17:22.209 --> 00:17:24.111 position:10% line:89% align:start
Did you hear a ghost talking?

00:17:24.144 --> 00:17:26.046 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't know anything
about secret passageways.

00:17:26.079 --> 00:17:27.147 position:27% line:89% align:start
Damn it, old man!

00:17:27.180 --> 00:17:28.650 position:13% line:83% align:start
Why are you trying to mess
with my head

00:17:28.683 --> 00:17:29.651 position:21% line:89% align:start
at a time like this?

00:17:29.684 --> 00:17:31.753 position:21% line:83% align:start
You came here through
that secret passageway

00:17:31.786 --> 00:17:32.820 position:27% line:89% align:start
just like I did!

00:17:32.854 --> 00:17:34.054 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:17:36.490 --> 00:17:38.125 position:27% line:89% align:start
Wait a second...

00:17:38.158 --> 00:17:41.829 position:19% line:83% align:start
S--Something about you
just seems off...

00:17:41.863 --> 00:17:43.363 position:35% line:89% align:start
Your wound.

00:17:43.397 --> 00:17:45.900 position:19% line:83% align:start
What the hell happened
to that bullet wound you had?

00:17:45.934 --> 00:17:47.100 position:38% line:89% align:start
A wound?

00:17:47.134 --> 00:17:49.504 position:21% line:83% align:start
Johngalli A. shot you
in your left shoulder.

00:17:49.537 --> 00:17:50.638 position:38% line:89% align:start
I saw it.

00:17:50.672 --> 00:17:54.107 position:27% line:83% align:start
And yet your arm
isn't bleeding... at all.

00:17:54.141 --> 00:17:56.376 position:19% line:89% align:start
[gasps] What? Mine too!

00:17:56.410 --> 00:17:58.445 position:27% line:83% align:start
My gunshot wound
just disappeared!

00:17:59.246 --> 00:18:00.848 position:16% line:89% align:start
[gasps] And who is this?

00:18:01.783 --> 00:18:04.351 position:5% line:89% align:start
[gasps] That isn't Johngalli A.!

00:18:04.384 --> 00:18:06.153 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's one of the guards!

00:18:06.186 --> 00:18:08.288 position:7% line:83% align:start
But... I thought he'd been shot
in the head

00:18:08.322 --> 00:18:09.624 position:21% line:89% align:start
in the visiting room!

00:18:09.657 --> 00:18:11.559 position:13% line:89% align:start
No sign of a wound at all.

00:18:11.593 --> 00:18:13.995 position:27% line:83% align:start
What gunshots are
you talking about?

00:18:14.028 --> 00:18:15.964 position:21% line:83% align:start
And who the devil is
this "Johngalli A."?

00:18:15.997 --> 00:18:17.230 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:17.264 --> 00:18:21.035 position:13% line:83% align:start
What the hell is happening?
This can't be right.

00:18:21.069 --> 00:18:22.670 position:13% line:89% align:start
It doesn't make any sense!

00:18:23.370 --> 00:18:24.371 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:28.076 --> 00:18:30.177 position:13% line:89% align:start
What the hell is going on?!

00:18:38.352 --> 00:18:40.722 position:21% line:83% align:start
I know that something
even more unfortunate

00:18:40.755 --> 00:18:42.557 position:19% line:89% align:start
than death will occur.

00:18:42.590 --> 00:18:44.892 position:30% line:83% align:start
No matter what,
you absolutely cannot go

00:18:44.926 --> 00:18:45.960 position:21% line:89% align:start
to the visiting room.

00:18:45.994 --> 00:18:47.160 position:21% line:89% align:start
The visiting room...

00:18:47.194 --> 00:18:50.497 position:16% line:83% align:start
That's right. It was odd
right from the start!

00:18:51.065 --> 00:18:52.165 position:33% line:89% align:start
My handcuffs.

00:18:52.199 --> 00:18:54.068 position:16% line:89% align:start
When did they disappear?

00:18:54.102 --> 00:18:56.403 position:24% line:83% align:start
And that bullet...
I'd been shot!

00:18:56.436 --> 00:18:58.405 position:24% line:83% align:start
But did any of that
really happen?

00:19:00.140 --> 00:19:01.042 position:30% line:89% align:start
Neither myself

00:19:01.075 --> 00:19:02.510 position:13% line:89% align:start
nor Dad are even wounded...

00:19:03.310 --> 00:19:05.479 position:27% line:83% align:start
Did Johngalli A.
even attack us?

00:19:05.513 --> 00:19:07.515 position:10% line:83% align:start
I can't keep things straight
anymore.

00:19:08.549 --> 00:19:11.653 position:33% line:83% align:start
How strange.
None of this makes any sense!

00:19:15.790 --> 00:19:17.324 position:24% line:89% align:start
This isn't reality!

00:19:18.191 --> 00:19:20.528 position:16% line:89% align:start
I must be hallucinating.

00:19:20.561 --> 00:19:23.163 position:35% line:83% align:start
Or else...
it's someone else's doing!

00:19:23.196 --> 00:19:24.364 position:41% line:89% align:start
No way.

00:19:25.099 --> 00:19:26.166 position:38% line:89% align:start
Stop it!

00:19:27.769 --> 00:19:30.071 position:35% line:89% align:start
[dripping]

00:19:30.104 --> 00:19:31.706 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:19:33.407 --> 00:19:34.509 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:19:36.711 --> 00:19:37.712 position:21% line:89% align:start
[dripping continues]

00:19:41.115 --> 00:19:42.182 position:38% line:89% align:start
