00:19:49.456 --> 00:19:50.825 position:38% line:89% align:start
[oozing]

00:19:53.528 --> 00:19:56.296 position:19% line:83% align:start
Looks like I really did
beat up that guard though.

00:19:56.864 --> 00:19:57.899 position:21% line:89% align:start
I guess that's real.

00:19:59.600 --> 00:20:01.869 position:24% line:83% align:start
This is a photo of
Johngalli A...

