the accident

00:20:09.177 --> 00:20:10.878 position:21% line:89% align:start
with the hitchhiker.

00:20:10.912 --> 00:20:12.847 position:27% line:83% align:start
How Johngalli A.
set it all up...

00:20:13.881 --> 00:20:14.716 position:33% line:89% align:start
back then...

00:20:15.683 --> 00:20:16.517 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's real.

00:20:17.451 --> 00:20:19.987 position:21% line:89% align:start
After that, I got up

00:20:20.021 --> 00:20:22.355 position:10% line:89% align:start
