out of the visiting room

00:20:36.938 --> 00:20:38.405 position:27% line:89% align:start
since I got here.

00:20:39.272 --> 00:20:40.440 position:33% line:89% align:start
That means...

00:20:42.076 --> 00:20:43.611 position:19% line:89% align:start
My mind made it all up?

00:20:44.212 --> 00:20:45.747 position:21% line:89% align:start
Johngalli A.'s Stand?

00:20:45.780 --> 00:20:48.315 position:27% line:83% align:start
All that bullshit
about air currents?

00:20:52.452 --> 00:20:54.088 position:19% line:89% align:start
The secret passageway,

00:20:54.122 --> 00:20:55.857 position:21% line:89% align:start
and what followed...

00:20:55.890 --> 00:20:58.793 position:13% line:83% align:start
From the moment we stepped
into this visitation room,

00:20:59.459 --> 00:21:00.795 position:24% line:89% align:start
we fell into a trap

00:21:01.796 --> 00:21:04.264 position:33% line:83% align:start
and have been
hallucinating ever since...

00:21:05.398 --> 00:21:07.334 position:24% line:89% align:start
Slowly, but surely,

00:21:07.367 --> 00:21:09.837 position:21% line:83% align:start
as if we were sitting
in a huge snake's stomach,

00:21:10.872 --> 00:21:12.039 position:21% line:89% align:start
