00:21:13.040 --> 00:21:14.441 position:27% line:83% align:start
The boy hiding in
the trash can,

00:21:14.474 --> 00:21:15.910 position:16% line:89% align:start
who gave me this bone...

00:21:16.711 --> 00:21:17.779 position:35% line:89% align:start
He's real!

00:21:19.947 --> 00:21:21.582 position:38% line:83% align:start
I woke up
from this nightmare

00:21:22.482 --> 00:21:24.819 position:19% line:83% align:start
because I hurt my hand
on this bone.

00:21:25.452 --> 00:21:27.255 position:16% line:89% align:start
Without this sharp pain,

00:21:27.287 --> 00:21:29.257 position:16% line:83% align:start
I would've stayed asleep
and died!

00:21:29.289 --> 00:21:30.423 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cracks]

00:21:31.225 --> 00:21:33.293 position:16% line:89% align:start
This power of illusions.

00:21:33.326 --> 00:21:35.930 position:33% line:83% align:start
This must be
Johngalli A.'s actual Stand!

00:21:39.133 --> 00:21:40.067 position:27% line:89% align:start
[screams in pain]

00:21:40.101 --> 00:21:41.102 position:38% line:89% align:start
[hisses]

00:21:41.135 --> 00:21:43.604 position:35% line:83% align:start
My thread.
I can't keep it together!

00:21:46.207 --> 00:21:47.340 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, shit!

00:21:48.709 --> 00:21:49.777 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:21:49.811 --> 00:21:50.711 position:38% line:89% align:start
Damn it.

00:21:51.779 --> 00:21:53.014 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm tired,

00:21:53.047 --> 00:21:54.982 position:7% line:89% align:start
but I can't go to sleep again.

00:21:55.016 --> 00:21:55.883 position:41% line:89% align:start
No way.

00:21:56.684 --> 00:21:58.619 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm not going out like this.

00:22:00.755 --> 00:22:03.624 position:19% line:83% align:start
We have to escape from
this god damn room!

00:22:05.126 --> 00:22:07.762 position:21% line:89% align:start
[grunting in effort]

00:22:08.328 --> 00:22:10.097 position:35% line:89% align:start
[straining]

00:22:10.131 --> 00:22:14.068 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:22:14.735 --> 00:22:18.639 position:33% line:89% align:start
Stone Ocean!

